org.apache.flink.streaming.api.functions.source

接口 ParallelSourceFunction<OUT>

  • 类型参数:
    OUT - The type of the records produced by this source.
    所有超级接口:
    Function, java.io.Serializable, SourceFunction<OUT>
    所有已知实现类:
    FlinkKafkaConsumer010, FlinkKafkaConsumer011, FlinkKafkaConsumer08, FlinkKafkaConsumer081, FlinkKafkaConsumer082, FlinkKafkaConsumer09, FlinkKafkaConsumerBase, FromSplittableIteratorFunction, GroupedProcessingTimeWindowExample.DataSource, InputFormatSourceFunction, NiFiSource, RichParallelSourceFunction, SpoutWrapper, StatefulSequenceSource

    @Public
public interface ParallelSourceFunction<OUT>
extends SourceFunction<OUT>
    A stream data source that is executed in parallel. Upon execution, the runtime will execute as many parallel instances of this function function as configured parallelism of the source.

    This interface acts only as a marker to tell the system that this source may be executed in parallel. When different parallel instances are required to perform different tasks, use the RichParallelSourceFunction to get access to the runtime context, which reveals information like the number of parallel tasks, and which parallel task the current instance is.
